Extensão Add Custom Search Engines
1. Obtenha a extensão no link abaixo
https://addons.mozilla.org/pt-BR/firefox/addon/add-custom-search-engine/
2. Configure a extensão adicionando os mecanismos de busca abaixo
Name: OpenSubtitles 		                            Search URL: https://www.opensubtitles.org/pb/search2/sublanguageid-por,pob/moviename-%s                       		Icon: https://www.opensubtitles.org/favicon.ico
Name: Legendas.TV			                            Search URL: http://legendas.tv/busca/%s                                                     						Icon: http://legendas.tv/favicon.ico
Name: YIFY Subtitles		                            Search URL: https://yifysubtitles.org/search?q=%s                                                 					Icon: https://yifysubtitles.org/favicon.ico
Name: YIFY Torrents			                            Search URL: https://yts.mx/browse-movies/%s/all/all/0/latest/0/all		                                        	Icon: /usr/share/icons/yts.png
Name: 1337x Torrents    	                          	Search URL: https://1337x.to/search/%s/1/								                                            Icon: https://1337x.to/favicon.ico
Name: IMDb					                            Search URL: https://www.imdb.com/find?q=%s								                                        	Icon: https://www.imdb.com/favicon.ico
Name: Zoom					                            Search URL: https://www.zoom.com.br/search?q=%s							                                        	Icon: https://www.zoom.com.br/favicon.ico
Name: Naughtyblog                                   	Search URL: https://www.naughtyblog.org/?s=%s							                                            Icon: https://www.naughtyblog.org/favicon.ico
Name: Google Tradutor    	                          	Search URL: https://translate.google.com.br/?hl=pt-BR&tab=wT#view=home&op=translate&sl=auto&tl=pt&text=%s     		Icon: https://translate.google.com.br/favicon.ico

